guardians.model.entities

Class CycleChange

  • java.lang.Object
    • guardians.model.entities.CycleChange

  • @Entity
 @ValidDayMonthYear
 @ValidCycleChange
public class CycleChange
extends java.lang.Object
    The CycleChange Entity is used to represent that two Doctor have changed their cycle shift a certain day of a certain Calendar Note the primary key used for this Entity is composite. Hence, the IdClass annotation is used. Moreover, CycleChange is a weak entity, so it receives its primary key from the corresponding DayConfiguration
    Author:
    miggoncan

        private Doctor cycleReceiver
        The cycle receiver is the Doctor that will take the cycle shift. Hence, although the cycleReceiver would not have had a cycle-shift this day, they will have it.
